{"word":"στέλλω","slug":"στέλλω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>στέλλω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Skt.\">Skt.</a>; <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on ideas relating to preparing and equipping] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a>; <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> the primary idea of preparing for <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> it is a short step to ‘take care in advance’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> be on guard, guard against <a href='B:540 8:20'>2 Cor 8:20</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> be wary of, stay away from <a href='B:600 3:6'>2 Th 3:6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:στεῖρα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:στέμμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}